<p>I like the designing of G-STAR RAW, there are always enough details to delight me. These are the two G-STAR RAW stores I visited most frequently:</p>

<h2>Grand Gateway Plaza</h2>

<ul>
<li>Address: F2 Grand Gateway Plaza, #1 Hongqiao Road</li>
<li>Metro: Line 1, Xu Jia Hui</li>
</ul>

<p>This is the flagship store in Shanghai.</p>

<h2>Raffles City</h2>

<ul>
<li>Address: F1 Raffles City, #268 Middle Xi Zang Road</li>
<li>Metro: Line 1 and Line 2, People Square</li>
</ul>

<h2>Discounts</h2>

<p>If you buy $500 or more at one time, you'll get a VIP discount card, that can make you save 20%.</p>